THANK YOU KO JAPAN !!!!

Very friendly guy. recently started getting pretty close to you as you have joined Apollo. you are underrated as a player i feel - people dont seem to appreciate your performance well in scrims good enough and i believe its a crucial part of evolving as a player and a trial especially - is being given positive feedback when you do good.
